"{\"uid\": \"thesouthafrican.com-sport-paris-olympics-2024-five-cool-facts-about-legendary-south-african-olympian-tatjana-smith-paris-olympics\", \"entities\": [{\"sentence\": \"Copyright Blue Sky Publications (Pty) Ltd. All Rights Reserved.\", \"from\": 0, \"to\": 63, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 15, \"end\": 18, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Sky_Sports\", \"score\": 0.9404248854060774, \"rank\": 0.06334760244690786, \"text\": \"Sky\", \"types\": [\"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\", \"Q15265344\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Sky_Sports\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Sky_Sports\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"thesouthafrican.com is a division of Blue Sky Publications Ltd. Reproduction without permission prohibited  Home\\u00bbSport\\u00bbParis Olympics 2024\\u00bbFive cool facts about legendary South African Olympian Tatjana Smith  South Africa's most decorated Olympian.\", \"from\": 65, \"to\": 313, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 107, \"end\": 110, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Sky_Sports\", \"score\": 0.9404248854060774, \"rank\": 0.06334760244690786, \"text\": \"Sky\", \"types\": [\"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\", \"Q15265344\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Sky_Sports\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Sky_Sports\"}, {\"begin\": 274, \"end\": 286, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/South_Africa\", \"score\": 0.9999999999463398, \"rank\": 5.276080080501918e-11, \"text\": \"South Africa\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/South_Africa\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/South_Africa\"}, {\"begin\": 304, \"end\": 312, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Olympic_Games\", \"score\": 0.9999999998417479, \"rank\": 1.5814838817209112e-10, \"text\": \"Olympian\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Olympic_Games\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Olympic_Games\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The coolest fact about Paris 2024 Olympics hero Tatjana Smith is she's the most decorated Olympian in South African history.\", \"from\": 315, \"to\": 439, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 405, \"end\": 413, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Olympic_Games\", \"score\": 0.9999999998417479, \"rank\": 1.5814838817209112e-10, \"text\": \"Olympian\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Olympic_Games\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Olympic_Games\"}, {\"begin\": 423, \"end\": 438, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/History_of_Africa\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"African history\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/History_of_Africa\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/History_of_Africa\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"There are more though.\", \"from\": 440, \"to\": 462, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Info viaolympics.com'sofficial website.\", \"from\": 464, \"to\": 503, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"My love for swimming makes me want to get up every morning and go to training.\", \"from\": 505, \"to\": 584, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"It's like my second home.\", \"from\": 585, \"to\": 610, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Being fortunate enough to travel the world doing what I love, seeing new places and meeting new people and sports heroes, motivates me a lot.\", \"from\": 611, \"to\": 752, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"The most important thing every young swimmer should realise is that nothing is impossible.\", \"from\": 753, \"to\": 843, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"They only need to believe and be prepared to put in the long and hard hours.\\\"\", \"from\": 844, \"to\": 921, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Reflecting on missing qualification for the 200m breaststroke in Rio, Smith was typically upbeat about one of the biggest setbacks in her professional career.\", \"from\": 923, \"to\": 1081, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 988, \"end\": 991, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/2016_Summer_Olympics\", \"score\": 0.9999712256278026, \"rank\": 2.877520016558025e-05, \"text\": \"Rio\", \"types\": [\"Q1656682\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/2016_Summer_Olympics\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/2016_Summer_Olympics\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"2016 was a bit of a disappointment, but I knew everything happens for a reason.\", \"from\": 1083, \"to\": 1163, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"I wasn't ready at that time.\", \"from\": 1164, \"to\": 1192, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"We got our hopes up and then I kind of got a dip, creating all that expectation.\", \"from\": 1193, \"to\": 1273, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"My fall was quite big, and I had to try and fall in love with the sport again.\", \"from\": 1274, \"to\": 1352, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"Looking back, maybe I needed to go through that disappointment to take me where I was in 2021 - more of a confident swimmer.\\\"\", \"from\": 1354, \"to\": 1480, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"Focus on one's improvement and one's own goals rather than comparing oneself to others.\", \"from\": 1482, \"to\": 1570, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"If you are constantly improving, you will eventually get to the top.\", \"from\": 1571, \"to\": 1639, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"For me, it was always about improving my time.\\\"\", \"from\": 1640, \"to\": 1687, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"21-year-old Letsile Tebogoproduced the run of his life to claim gold in a much-anticipated 200m event.\", \"from\": 1689, \"to\": 1791, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"He was the fastest qualifier and the only man to go under 20 seconds in the semi-finals, so he was certainly expected to medal.\", \"from\": 1792, \"to\": 1919, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"However, 100m champion andAmerican superstar Noah Lyleswas the overwhelming favourite to claim gold alongside his compatriot Kenny Bednarek.\", \"from\": 1920, \"to\": 2060, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2045, \"end\": 2059, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Kenny_Bednarek\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Kenny Bednarek\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Kenny_Bednarek\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Kenny_Bednarek\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"However, Tebogo ripped up the script and stormed to the line first in 19.46 seconds ahead of Bednarek in 19.62 and Lyles in 19.70.\", \"from\": 2061, \"to\": 2191, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2176, \"end\": 2181, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Jordan_Lyles\", \"score\": 0.9995308743345979, \"rank\": 0.0003411168687177989, \"text\": \"Lyles\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\", \"Q10871364\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Jordan_Lyles\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Jordan_Lyles\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Tebogo is the first African man to win this event and it's the first gold medal in Botswana's history at the Olympic Games.\", \"from\": 2192, \"to\": 2315, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2275, \"end\": 2283, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Botswana\", \"score\": 0.9999999999863576, \"rank\": 1.3723055044245615e-11, \"text\": \"Botswana\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Botswana\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Botswana\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Touchingly, Tebogo revealed the birthdate of his late mother on his running shoes in the moments after claiming what must have been a truly emotional victory.\", \"from\": 2316, \"to\": 2474, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Tebogo followed this trailblazing success up with gold at a recent Diamond League meeting in Switzerland.\", \"from\": 2476, \"to\": 2581, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2543, \"end\": 2557, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Diamond_League\", \"score\": 0.9999104005821517, \"rank\": 8.586545755056552e-05, \"text\": \"Diamond League\", \"types\": [\"Q623109\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Diamond_League\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Diamond_League\"}, {\"begin\": 2569, \"end\": 2580, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Switzerland\", \"score\": 0.7560293521076055, \"rank\": 0.3226825597730762, \"text\": \"Switzerland\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Switzerland\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Switzerland\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"He eased across the line in 19.64 seconds for another win.\", \"from\": 2582, \"to\": 2640, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"He's in the form of his life.\", \"from\": 2641, \"to\": 2670, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Let us know by clicking on the comment tab below this article or emailinginfo@thesouthafrican.com.\", \"from\": 2672, \"to\": 2770, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"You can also send a WhatsApp to 060 011 021 1.\", \"from\": 2771, \"to\": 2817, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2791, \"end\": 2799, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/WhatsApp\", \"score\": 0.9892455330390911, \"rank\": 0.010871382888897725, \"text\": \"WhatsApp\", \"types\": [\"Q7397\", \"Q386724\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/WhatsApp\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/WhatsApp\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Follow@TheSAnews on XandThe South African on Facebookfor your social fix.\", \"from\": 2818, \"to\": 2891, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"WIN R2 000: Take The South African's SASSA Survey  The South African is hiring!\", \"from\": 2893, \"to\": 2972, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2893, \"end\": 2896, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/WIN_Television\", \"score\": 0.999900844269613, \"rank\": 9.916333385842119e-05, \"text\": \"WIN\", \"types\": [\"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\", \"Q15265344\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/WIN_Television\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/WIN_Television\"}, {\"begin\": 2897, \"end\": 2899, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/DVD_regio